  "keyFeatures": [
    "70+ chart types with 2D and 3D views",
    "VCL and FireMonkey (FMX) framework support",
    "Real-time data visualization and animations",
    "Financial charts (Candle, MACD, Volume, RSI)",
    "Statistical charts (Histogram, Box Plot, Error Bars)",
    "Interactive gauges and circular gauges",
